                    <desc>
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#85r" facs="087">fols. 85r, </locus>);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#2r #64r #72v" facs="007 068 077">2r, 64r, 72v</locus>).
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
